title: GET_HELI_THROTTLE_CONTROL
content:
0x8E86238D// GetHeliThrottleControl
float GET_HELI_THROTTLE_CONTROL(Vehicle heli);Parameters:heli: The helicopter to check.Returns: Returns a value representing the throttle control of the helicopter. The value ranges from 0.0 (no throttle) to 2.0 (full throttle).
